  "prompt": "Can I use my VSP insurance to purchase glasses at LensCrafters?",
  "response": "Yes, you can typically use VSP (Vision Service Plan) insurance to purchase glasses at LensCrafters. LensCrafters is an in-network provider for VSP, meaning you can use your insurance benefits there. However, it's always a good idea to verify with your specific VSP plan and LensCrafters location to ensure they accept your insurance and to understand what costs will be covered. Contact your VSP customer service or the LensCrafters store directly to get detailed information about your coverage.",
